Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So good to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm in a bit of a dilemma, and I need some clarification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've learned from you that holding something in mind and intention
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,can increase the likelihood of potentiality actualizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Probability, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a probability.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is an idea current right now among certain spiritual communities
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that faith and belief can have something to do with increasing likelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The faith and belief of the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in great conflict about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you've just resolved the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've resolved the whole thing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be one of the local conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In an experiment of having a person who's, you know, at the bottom of the box, hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, even the ones who are in jail or in institutions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,who maybe even have brain defects that can't allow them to, you know, learn from their experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think would happen if you put them in a cell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and just played Kyrie for them for a month, some music?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder because it would help me understand the effects of the whole thing and maybe some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A hypothetical case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And another arena, but people who do archaeology,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:03:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd still be able to find remnants or remains of Christ's servants, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,like disciples or the apostles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything left there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one I've done is the bones of St. Peter under the altar in the Basilica in Rome, calibrated 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Unrecovered, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they all been recovered from under the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And they calibrated 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That pretty much indicates that it was one of the apostles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about the experiencer versus the witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other night I had a dream which I thought was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning when I awakened, there was a part of me analyzing the dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,another part simultaneously singing the chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, hear my prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then a third part that came up, an inner voice that said, Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know that the analyzer was the experiencer or the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What were the other parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that you can label them that distinctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena were occurring spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thing that you got about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all spontaneously emerging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not contrived, but spontaneous, unfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are just different ways of looking at the clock, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a different clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to release the experiencing of experience than the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the experiencer hypothetically proposes an independent agent, a personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an experiencer who's experiencing and witnessing the experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nobody doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank both of you for all you've done for me in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And last fall, you told me that I have lifetimes of anger built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been doing what you have said about being angrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I have been doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the middle, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a couple of holes in my backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it going to take me lifetimes to get rid of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can uncork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's coming up is anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's holding the anger down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fear of the anger, guilt over the anger, reluctance to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let go and let it be okay to be angry and enjoy it, keep saying more, I want more of it, more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel the anger coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you'll run out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, why your anger will come up, what you're angry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you release that, that stops the anger in the first place, you see, because you're not angry for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll have to get rid of the resentment of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you're angry at God, too, because if it wasn't for this God, you wouldn't be going through the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to forgive yourself and forgive divinity and see that it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the automatic evolution of consciousness itself unfolding in that particular curly way there, right in that corner of your life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to hurry it up and get it over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you let go resisting it, you know, let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So every little bit of anger, I feel, just be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it could be almost all the time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you let go resisting it, you'll run it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll eventually run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be fed all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And something is feeding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll certainly jump in your mind what it's being fed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel you're being blamed for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're furious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you didn't get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's probably some karmic propensity there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blamed for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been deprived of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Some more basic anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry at being reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a human being again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just dig holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me heaven and here I am back on earth again, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mad as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably scared to look at being angry at God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but that may be part of it, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's the ultimate responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the ultimate one responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, a lot of us unconsciously blame God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to do it consciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a lecture a few months ago on DVD or CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody asked about calibrating Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And after the questioning and sort of brief answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,saying that it's kind of a difficult thing to answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned vortexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a curiosity I have is what about the vortexes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So far I have, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all airy-fairy and new agey and woo-woo-woo and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see spaceships floating in and out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to just discontinue that prairie ride, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If they had magic in them, there'd be enlightened people all over Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading the nitwit news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the eighth , the piece of paper logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sedona eccentric or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Another question I had about Siemens Mor, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Relativism, yeah, yes, yeah, yeah, so that's sort of,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be infiltrating currently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's bringing down the calibration, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have some, I have some fear about what the outcome is of that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was asked to discuss, you know, plant ret colleague Enlightenmentics,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,about what the outcome is going to be why should you be afraid you're not god it's not your
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,responsibility probably a lot of people are going to go off the road and get wrecked okay
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,see the seduction the seduction of it see the spiritual seeker is naive doesn't realize he's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,being surrounded by seduction all the time the buddha mentions it directly i myself have been
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,have been experienced it directly that the higher you get the more that which oppose which is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,opposed that divinity love and god's truth will come up and attack you actually okay so it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to be seduction through various means yes to be more that the demand is to be more steadfast in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,your conviction to the truth that's all okay i can do that but don't yeah i mean you will be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,challenged i don't like to bring it up because it makes people paranoid all right but there will
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,come up a time when you actually realize that you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are being challenged by the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty unbelievable. Sounds like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a fairy book, but it happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I don't believe what's happening, but it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, if that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when that comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe pray for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,protection or guidance? Refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Refuse, okay. It's your karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,entitlement
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequent of this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,human lifetime, you already
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,have the karmic entitlement to refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're karmically entitled to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,get thee hence, Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. No, you're entitled to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,refuse it, rebuke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it comes as a shock. You don't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening for a little while
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because it seems so outlandish and bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really believe that this is actually
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,happening in your own
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime. But I've been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,confronted with it in its barest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a photo of you, too, without her in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, smile, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mario.
