Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
