Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Journey's out of the body? Yes. Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this.
