Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like an angel speaking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something just wonderful about his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope you're not off sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because I brought you a belated Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see if we can find a volunteer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we were here in June, and I came
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,up and had given you a gift then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just had to come up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To have a glance from a person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with unconditional love into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd love to thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a nice messenger for Bob,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, he had the most magical voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll never forget when I read his book
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd had out-of-body experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody talked about it in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Near-death experiences, out-of-body,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's his book by Monroe.
