Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,comes back in his body, and there's his dutiful wife
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,lying next to him, and he's guilt-stricken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then with a scientific engineering mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,he sets about trying to figure out how to set it up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to create an altered state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the altered state of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you can leave the body at will, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was fun.
