Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to go out-of-body in a group
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and decide where we were going to meet in various domains, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
