Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, in a way, I've sort of avoided it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with academic tradition.
