Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you can retain it longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true.
