Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask your forgiveness for the wrongs that i've done in this life and in all of all of life and i
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to ask if you would if you here's what you do you pray to god you surrender to god
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you i would do the 12 steps like they do in a we were admitted we were powerless
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,over the mistakes we've made turned our life over to god made a thorough moral inventory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,made a decision to correct the things that we could correct did this on a daily basis and then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,sought through prayer and supplication to increase our conscious contact with god
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing more you can do no matter what pathway you choose because all the pathways are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,going to boil down to that because that's a line with inner honesty yeah thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yep that's very good yes you know your forgiveness comes from yourself and god god does you said that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you were forgiven when you choose uh you choose jesus christ as your savior right so when you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,choose jesus christ as your savior then you must have faith and that that jesus christ will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,stand for you before the father those who turn to me i will speak for before the father so put faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in those words and they will become yours and do the 91st psalm when you get bored with all that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,hi doc yeah hi you've you've talked a lot about the importance of surrendering thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrendering thoughts as they arise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've spoken of how the mind can come up with thoughts faster than we can surrender them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you could share with us about how to work with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the process of thinkingness itself and not thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because thoughts are individual and it will create endless arrays of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go wanting of thinkingness itself, to see that it's of no value.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it's coming up because you want it to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:24:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could let go the basic motive behind thinkingness, not the thoughts because they're by the millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But thinkingness itself, first of all, gives you a sense of continuity of a doer, of an I, a separate I within.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that the secret payoff is that there's a separate individual I having all these thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it confirms the self as a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.24,0:24:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that one through.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.36,0:24:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You just look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Play with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.61,0:24:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.92,0:24:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.92,0:24:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.07,0:24:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My question I think has to do with the spiritual ego, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.07,0:24:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm noticing more often that I'll start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.07,0:24:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be moved with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.07,0:24:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And no sooner am I into three seconds of crying and joy that I get real excited that I'm crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.07,0:25:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm joyful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.07,0:25:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, yeah, I'm like, I'm dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.17,0:25:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.17,0:25:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.17,0:25:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.17,0:25:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These phenomena come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.17,0:25:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.17,0:25:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it says to rate or evaluate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.17,0:25:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.17,0:25:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They come and they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.29,0:25:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.29,0:25:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered if it was like an addiction to the experience of joy or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.29,0:25:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the higher states.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.29,0:25:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.29,0:25:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.29,0:25:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.46,0:25:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They come to an end of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.72,0:25:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about getting hooked on the higher states.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.72,0:25:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.72,0:25:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.72,0:25:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because like joy will only run so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.98,0:25:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll see the end of joy that you have an option to cop out and to release it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.49,0:25:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.49,0:25:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask another question?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.74,0:26:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've mentioned, that reminded me, you say sometimes people will just sort of go along
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.74,0:26:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.74,0:26:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they'll stop at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.74,0:26:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.90,0:26:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I hold the intention of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do have that concern that if I do reach a level of joy as a dominant level, they'll
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,just.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.56,0:26:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuck in joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.56,0:26:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.56,0:26:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.56,0:26:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.56,0:26:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even in joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.56,0:26:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it back to the.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.56,0:26:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.56,0:26:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.56,0:26:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.56,0:26:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.56,0:26:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.75,0:26:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing has within itself the kernel of its own solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.75,0:26:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.75,0:26:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such an honor to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.75,0:26:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.09,0:26:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.09,0:26:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such an honor to be up here with both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.09,0:26:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really the reason I'm up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.09,0:26:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you answered my question about guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.09,0:26:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask about, you said in previous lectures that now is a very difficult time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.09,0:26:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a parent and have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.09,0:26:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.09,0:26:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As my husband and I are looking towards that, questioning that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.09,0:26:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if having children is compatible with the path towards enlightenment at this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.09,0:26:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,time?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.09,0:26:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thoughts on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.09,0:26:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I never looked at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.09,0:26:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.09,0:26:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.09,0:26:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.09,0:27:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.09,0:27:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.09,0:27:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.09,0:27:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.09,0:27:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.09,0:27:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.09,0:27:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.09,0:27:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.09,0:27:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.09,0:27:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.09,0:27:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, is it a distraction or is it an opportunity to further your skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.09,0:27:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.09,0:27:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be how you hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.38,0:27:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that the child advances your consciousness faster because you have to come to unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.81,0:27:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,love rather quickly and your fears about what might happen to the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.76,0:27:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it brings up a lot of things, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.31,0:27:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.31,0:27:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.31,0:27:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't really interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.64,0:27:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you were looking more at monastic-drivenness, then a child would be out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.94,0:27:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to join a holy order?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.48,0:27:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.16,0:27:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.16,0:27:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.79,0:28:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,More women are turning to it all of a sudden, I realize now, this illusion with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.93,0:28:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So those who turn to the holy orders in the past fell way down and now they're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.36,0:28:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,again it's interesting I came with a question from two of your students their
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.47,0:28:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,mother seems to go crazy maybe hearing voices and I was there and her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,personality was changed and her eyes were black and I tried the testing of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.22,0:28:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirits and it seemed to work she came back and her personality changed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.07,0:28:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,everything and she said she was not under control and very good but like
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.63,0:29:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,three or five days later it got worse and it seemed she's listening here now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.14,0:29:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,three three voices are you living with this person no no well what do you what's
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.66,0:29:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your involvement it's the matter of two of your students who are asking the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.01,0:29:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,question I'm here for to ask the question for them it's the mother of a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.00,0:29:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,couple of students asking the question
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.38,0:29:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,about who I'm the mother the mother of the students yeah what is the question
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,again is she possessed yeah what demonic possession right yeah could be and also
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.15,0:29:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what what the treatment could be if it's there's several pathways you can
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.13,0:29:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,approach it everything's physical mental and spiritual you get a pressure through
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.49,0:29:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the medical
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.34,0:29:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,she's hearing voices having hallucinations there's a drugs that will
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.39,0:30:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,block off hallucinations and psychotic symptoms yes she's getting neuroleptica
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.39,0:30:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,right now right neuroleptica medicine she's already to hear voices when
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.95,0:30:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nobody there is termed you know in medicine psychotic conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.39,0:30:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,usually often due to abnormal brain chemistry there's quite a few
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.07,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,medications that will correct the brain chemistry then see what's the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.01,0:30:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,other side effects of it and you know she's not going to be able to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.52,0:30:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly right because you're still there after that there was every psychotic
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.38,0:30:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,person isn't necessarily possessed we step I used to be in charge of a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.50,0:30:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,hospital we had five thousand of them yeah so if you just put everybody in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.03,0:30:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the hospital on an anti-psychotic drug you know about 35% would leave within a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.01,0:30:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,week or two all the symptoms would disappear did abnormal brain chemistry so
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.48,0:31:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest could have heavy duty karmic background and I don't think I'd get involved in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.48,0:31:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, yeah, but could you maybe calibrate if it's something else too, like if she's possessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.48,0:31:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that isn't the way to go about it. The way to go about it is to do it like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.53,0:31:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because possession is easy if you're mentally ill. Many mentally ill people are first mentally ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.43,0:31:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,first they've got negative karma, then they're mentally ill, then while mentally ill they then also get possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.83,0:31:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.30,0:31:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They hear God's voice talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.95,0:31:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The hospital used to be full of people with God's voice talking to them and cerebral syphilis was common.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.20,0:31:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we found penicillin. God talking to people disappeared, fell all the way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.20,0:31:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Napoleon disappeared, Jesus disappeared, all that disappeared from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.20,0:31:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything's physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.20,0:32:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical, mental, spiritual, I would take the simplest one first before you tackle the far more difficult and esoteric.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.55,0:32:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to get involved in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And could you tell me if I picked something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.88,0:32:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't pick anything up. You're too harmless. Nobody wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.14,0:32:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.79,0:32:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't even kill anybody. What kind of a capture would he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.55,0:32:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc. I'm reading your new book.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.55,0:32:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.55,0:32:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you're writing about value, projecting value onto things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.55,0:32:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the exercises you've given for like focusing on the periphery or focusing directly on a certain point have been very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.55,0:32:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if there's something similar, simple like that that I can use to help with the projecting value onto people or...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.14,0:33:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The projection of values?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.20,0:33:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.20,0:33:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the reality behind it is the perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.20,0:33:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute perfection of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.20,0:33:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So focus and pray about the capacity to discern the perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.20,0:33:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.83,0:33:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.83,0:33:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as the killer comes at you, you realize he's the perfect killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.96,0:33:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.40,0:33:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Craziness, knife, psychosis, hallucination, the ultimate spook coming at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.98,0:33:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So try to see the perfection of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.75,0:33:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that bypass that particularity and get more to the generality that eliminates the particularity, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.75,0:33:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See what we said about that, did we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.11,0:33:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me that it's beautiful or not beautiful or perfect or defective or what.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.11,0:33:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can say about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.15,0:33:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.15,0:34:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.09,0:34:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means is that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.79,0:34:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which it is shines forth in stunning perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.80,0:34:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you have to project upon it, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.59,0:34:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop describing things. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.59,0:34:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need to be described.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.80,0:34:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.80,0:34:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thinkingness, the thinkingness, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, that's its essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.34,0:34:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's how you feel about it and how you see it, that's perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.55,0:34:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritual awareness eventually focuses more and more on essence and less and less on appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.55,0:34:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.65,0:34:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For my work, I do some writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.86,0:34:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For a lady here, I'm writing her memoirs and it's very involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.86,0:34:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's very involved in description and I'm very locked into words and appearance, I guess, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.86,0:35:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine for that particular kind of work. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.86,0:35:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But just drop that when I walk away from the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.92,0:35:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.92,0:35:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.05,0:35:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.05,0:35:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay for work, but it's a distraction to your own personal evolution, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.05,0:35:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaboration on it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.50,0:35:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I write about that rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.50,0:35:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I could write a whole book about that rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.50,0:35:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means, what it signifies, what I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.82,0:35:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.82,0:35:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have recently identified a repetition of the same kind of relationship over and over and over in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.82,0:35:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to know if that is a past life thing and if it is, what I do if I identify what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.46,0:35:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's something, I just don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.46,0:35:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you look for the motive, you look for the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.46,0:35:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The motive in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.46,0:36:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look to see what the pattern is about yourself that repeats itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.48,0:36:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you need to see about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.55,0:36:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these destructive relationships?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.55,0:36:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.55,0:36:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.05,0:36:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not destructive, but they're a bit destructive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.09,0:36:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.09,0:36:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're destructive to me, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.09,0:36:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they destructive to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.09,0:36:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They just don't, they're not sort of, they're nothing that grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.15,0:36:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to grow on top of everything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.15,0:36:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, they're not, in some sense they're not even real.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.21,0:36:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm sort of projecting something in these relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.21,0:36:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not, so they don't sort of develop into real and creative, positive relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.21,0:36:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Relationships got to be creative?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.21,0:36:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You put a heap, a lot of stuff on your relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.21,0:36:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it's supposed to help you evolve, be creative, be exciting, and have meaning and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.21,0:37:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,significance?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.21,0:37:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.21,0:37:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from for the hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.34,0:37:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just be yourself and have some toast together in the morning and play the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.34,0:37:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.34,0:37:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fried eggs or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.71,0:37:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, does life have to be a major drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.71,0:37:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.71,0:37:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe I'm just misinterpreting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.71,0:37:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.71,0:37:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.71,0:37:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.71,0:37:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the end of the world, you're like, oh, that's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.71,0:37:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.71,0:37:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the intrinsic reality of a thing, you see each one is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.71,0:37:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.71,0:37:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.71,0:37:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.82,0:37:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.82,0:37:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What more could you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.65,0:37:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.65,0:37:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.65,0:37:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A person gives you a glance of trusting love.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.65,0:37:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing more in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.65,0:37:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What more is there in a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.65,0:37:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, what else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.88,0:37:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.88,0:37:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.88,0:37:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very nice to meet you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.88,0:37:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.88,0:37:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.88,0:37:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.86,0:37:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.86,0:37:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.86,0:37:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.86,0:38:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.65,0:38:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.65,0:38:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.80,0:38:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.80,0:38:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.80,0:38:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.80,0:38:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.80,0:38:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.80,0:38:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.80,0:38:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very, very grateful for your books and your DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.80,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relatively new to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.80,0:38:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I also find The Course in Miracles very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.76,0:38:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.76,0:38:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You answered my main question.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.42,0:38:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was autism-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.96,0:38:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard a question on The Course in Miracles and so I thought I'd ask you one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.36,0:38:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.40,0:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It relates to calibrations though.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.80,0:38:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.84,0:38:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My understanding is that Jesus dictated most of the course of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.17,0:38:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I read in Truth vs. Falsehood that the New Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.32,0:39:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,without the book of Revelations, calibrates very highly the high 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.11,0:39:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that the people at that time calibrated at about the 100 level.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.44,0:39:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And today in America, people calibrate at 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.07,0:39:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Course in Miracles, the textbook, calibrates around 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.80,0:39:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seems like a discrepancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.94,0:39:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How is there a discrepancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.13,0:39:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seemed like for people calibrating so highly today,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.17,0:39:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,why is Jesus' message, which was dictated and written immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.98,0:39:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to buy that whole story that it was dictated personally by Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.07,0:39:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus calibrates at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.65,0:39:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Miracles calibrates at 550 in the book, textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.46,0:39:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the workbook is 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.00,0:39:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So Jesus dictated it would calibrate at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.01,0:40:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's fudging a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.01,0:40:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it seems like.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.80,0:40:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think you're answering my question there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.42,0:40:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.11,0:40:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the voice probably said is they're speaking for Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.84,0:40:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very curious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.03,0:40:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That this is a spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.30,0:40:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That this is a spiritual pathway, speaking for Jesus, but not as Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.19,0:40:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.07,0:40:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any feeling for what exactly this voice is?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.55,0:40:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I knew Helen Schuchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.61,0:40:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And Helen got it at what she called interdictation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.76,0:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there's a similar case of interdictation that resulted in the books that are all bound in blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.03,0:40:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.67,0:40:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Alice Bailey also came interdictation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.98,0:40:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them are sources of a considerable amount of spiritual information.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.01,0:40:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How literally to take it, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.92,0:40:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.84,0:41:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one I referred to comes from the White Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you calibrate, is there a White Brotherhood, you'll get yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.44,0:41:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you say, what is their calibrated level, you get it's around 650.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.17,0:41:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's probably an area of heaven made up of people devoted to teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.46,0:41:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is their function, to respond to prayers and to requests for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.01,0:41:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.73,0:41:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be my guess what's going on, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.78,0:41:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm pretty close to the reality of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.50,0:41:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when you leave the body, you've got options.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.53,0:41:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not compelled to go anyplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.09,0:41:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're attracted to that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to learn and teach, then you would be attracted to a teaching brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.51,0:41:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So the White Brotherhood is made up of ascended teachers who serve better in their capacity currently than they would to reincarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.57,0:41:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean they won't reincarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.65,0:41:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean they won't reincarnate some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.21,0:41:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget, this civilization is going through evolutionary periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.19,0:42:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could wait on the other side to a time when your reappearance here would serve some higher purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.53,0:42:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you just get washed out with the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.55,0:42:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.61,0:42:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.67,0:42:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.03,0:42:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.59,0:42:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.34,0:42:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if what I said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.84,0:42:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What I said is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.69,0:42:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.61,0:42:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an intuitive knowing of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.92,0:42:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.63,0:42:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have options, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.90,0:42:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How best can I serve the old Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.32,0:42:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,By staying in the body, by refusing to come back into the body, or waiting for a better time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.82,0:42:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Timing is important in these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.00,0:42:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You come back at the wrong time, and you get wiped out, and your message is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.69,0:42:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.42,0:42:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.57,0:42:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.84,0:42:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I am a medical physician who quit my practice of 21 years last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.30,0:42:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.40,0:42:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.46,0:42:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.48,0:42:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.55,0:42:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.61,0:42:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.63,0:42:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.65,0:42:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.88,0:42:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.90,0:42:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.92,0:42:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
