Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the speech itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.50,0:53:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.50,0:53:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Speech itself. How speech itself came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.50,0:53:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, speech? Vocalization?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.50,0:53:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vocalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.50,0:53:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because I would, I assumed that I was the originator.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.50,0:53:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the vocalizer. Oh, I see. Okay. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.50,0:53:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.32,0:53:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.61,0:53:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm one, I was asked a question, who is speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.61,0:53:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.61,0:53:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't able to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.61,0:53:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.73,0:53:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.73,0:53:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.73,0:53:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.96,0:53:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.96,0:53:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anybody answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.96,0:53:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The answering is answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.96,0:53:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The answering is answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.94,0:53:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point to hypothecate an entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.94,0:53:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an imaginary entity that you'll then have to get rid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.21,0:53:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.21,0:53:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness responded to that situation
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.69,0:54:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,out of its autonomous nature as consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.69,0:54:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you happen to be in the way of it
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.46,0:54:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that you're the one that did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.42,0:54:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So if speech arises from pure consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.69,0:54:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes out less than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.19,0:54:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it that gets in the way of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.19,0:54:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the way you phrased the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.76,0:54:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.76,0:54:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the speaker when you speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.76,0:54:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you clear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.09,0:54:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.98,0:54:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you presume is the speaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.98,0:54:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me with a S.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.09,0:54:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.09,0:54:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.09,0:54:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.19,0:54:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an autonomous, separate I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.61,0:54:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that is always presumed to be the initiator of the action,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.61,0:54:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the locus of the sense of identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.78,0:54:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.78,0:54:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you identify that that's what thinks it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.11,0:55:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then you know what you need to transcend,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.63,0:55:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because no such entity exists in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.63,0:55:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the unraveling of that dilemma
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.13,0:55:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the point that you're at now,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.46,0:55:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,how to unravel that dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.46,0:55:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.46,0:55:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.30,0:55:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Any tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.30,0:55:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take a few decades, but you'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.57,0:55:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And doing of the sense of a personal self,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.57,0:55:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the initiator, the doer,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.57,0:55:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the responsible one,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.73,0:55:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,could take a lifetime, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.73,0:55:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise everybody would be enlightened, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.94,0:55:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're moving in the direction
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.94,0:55:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend that identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.94,0:55:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.94,0:55:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The quickest way through is to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.94,0:55:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing, observing,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.94,0:55:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and see that witnessing and observing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.94,0:55:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are phenomena that are happening without a personal I.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.94,0:55:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal I takes credit for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.50,0:55:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but the personal I is not witnessing or observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.51,0:56:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time the personal I catches onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.51,0:56:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing is over already.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.51,0:56:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So is the way to surrender that claim?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.51,0:56:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to transcend that illusion, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.73,0:56:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.30,0:56:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on witnessing and observing as a phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.59,0:56:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll become aware in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.59,0:56:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.59,0:56:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any I or me or self witnessing or observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.59,0:56:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The breathing of your nose is happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.13,0:56:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.13,0:56:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll breathe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.13,0:56:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think I'll breathe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.13,0:56:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.13,0:56:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.26,0:56:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just autonomous, automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.78,0:56:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So see the automaticness of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.78,0:56:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll see that it's an autonomous phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.78,0:56:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.40,0:56:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.40,0:56:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal I making a decision to be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.40,0:56:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.76,0:56:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens that way without asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.34,0:57:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.38,0:57:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all that you give us,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.38,0:57:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and thank you for your devotion to your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.38,0:57:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you know of our devotion to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.38,0:57:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.38,0:57:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.38,0:57:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am committed to being of service to humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.38,0:57:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I work with angelic realm energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.38,0:57:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if it's appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.38,0:57:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to just stay focused in living in the 500s
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.38,0:57:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.38,0:57:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's appropriate to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.38,0:57:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay living in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.38,0:57:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Living in the energy of the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.38,0:57:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.38,0:57:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.38,0:57:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.38,0:57:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that level,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.38,0:57:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,are we able to transcend karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.38,0:57:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You transcend karma every time you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.05,0:57:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is integrous over that which is not integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.05,0:57:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.05,0:57:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You whittle away at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.32,0:57:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You whittle away at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.32,0:57:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then pretty soon the whole bank falls down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.32,0:57:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said no to certain types of karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.86,0:57:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.86,0:57:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeatedly, they disappear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.09,0:58:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer feel tempted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.11,0:58:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.11,0:58:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.11,0:58:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And just a very quick question, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.11,0:58:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine is dying of cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.11,0:58:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's adopted the Dawkins philosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.11,0:58:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the God delusion as her truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.11,0:58:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.11,0:58:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything I can do to help her to find peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.53,0:58:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's found peace
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.53,0:58:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,through a secularized version.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.53,0:58:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So what she perceives is that she will be extinguished,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.53,0:58:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that the personal self will disappear into oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.53,0:58:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.53,0:58:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's looking forward to oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.53,0:58:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's looking forward to oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.78,0:58:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she wants oblivion and loves oblivion
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.78,0:58:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and chooses oblivion,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.78,0:58:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll experience oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.98,0:58:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And oblivion is terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.03,0:58:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So if that's what works for her, we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.05,0:58:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make it personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.05,0:58:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.05,0:58:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She would stay there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.61,0:59:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But because it's not the ultimate reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.61,0:59:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't stay there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.61,0:59:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.11,0:59:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oblivion is not the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.11,0:59:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So she'll transcend that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.11,0:59:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can stay there for a few thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.11,0:59:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get bored with oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.17,0:59:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what karmically brought it back
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.17,0:59:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that I came into this world in oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.17,0:59:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And frankly, I was reluctant to see it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.17,0:59:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.65,0:59:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't happy to realize that I existed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.65,0:59:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a shock, not pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.48,0:59:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So if oblivion is what she chooses,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.48,0:59:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so let it be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.48,0:59:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.53,0:59:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.53,0:59:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.53,0:59:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.53,0:59:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.53,0:59:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Many blessings to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.53,0:59:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been taking too much of his work on lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.53,0:59:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bumming around while we do all the stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.53,0:59:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's doing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.53,0:59:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,kicking his toes in the clouds or what.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.38,0:59:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.78,0:59:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if she chooses oblivion, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.78,1:00:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.17,1:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's being honest about her choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.38,1:00:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being honest about her choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.38,1:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's done a lot of self-examination.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.38,1:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a self-admitted, honest atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.38,1:00:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So let her be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.38,1:00:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.34,1:00:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.34,1:00:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.34,1:00:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.34,1:00:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.92,1:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place where honest atheists go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.98,1:00:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They go to science college up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.98,1:00:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.15,1:00:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Write papers on erudite subjects.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.15,1:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.86,1:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend in California
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.86,1:00:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,asked me to say that she sends her love,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.86,1:00:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,praise, and gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.86,1:00:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.86,1:00:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, while on retreat,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.86,1:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that came up over and over,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.86,1:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how does one transcend the basic,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.86,1:00:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what feels like a basic need of touch?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.86,1:00:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Basic need of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.92,1:00:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.92,1:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.92,1:00:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.92,1:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like if you're, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.92,1:01:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the child, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.92,1:01:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The child constantly looking for reassurance
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.07,1:01:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the animal looking for orientation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.07,1:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.42,1:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.42,1:01:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.51,1:01:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does one look at the child?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.51,1:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like do the inner child type thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.51,1:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the child within you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.61,1:01:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.61,1:01:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.61,1:01:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the adult.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.61,1:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this adult sure does feel like she needs to be touched.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.61,1:01:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.61,1:01:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about doing something yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.61,1:01:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.61,1:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.61,1:01:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.00,1:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.00,1:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel like you have to touch everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.00,1:01:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when you talk to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.00,1:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.00,1:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.00,1:01:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just talking about while in retreat
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.00,1:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,where I haven't been,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.00,1:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't had like,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.00,1:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.00,1:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.00,1:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.00,1:01:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.00,1:01:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.00,1:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.00,1:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.00,1:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had like normal everyday affection hugs
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.00,1:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever like I'm used to.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.00,1:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.00,1:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And just it's noticing it and going,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.00,1:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,well, how do you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.00,1:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.00,1:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.00,1:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.00,1:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.00,1:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so if I look at the child,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.00,1:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,do I need to look at my child?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.00,1:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's where it's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.00,1:01:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.00,1:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.00,1:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.40,1:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,any suggestions for that or?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.40,1:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, grow it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.40,1:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.40,1:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.40,1:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't have cookies and milk every day after school.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.40,1:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.40,1:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.40,1:02:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.40,1:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you got me on my cookies.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.40,1:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.40,1:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,man.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.40,1:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a mean world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.07,1:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.07,1:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.07,1:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.07,1:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody's a huggy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.07,1:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.07,1:02:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.07,1:02:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.07,1:02:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,no,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.07,1:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,no,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.07,1:02:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not everybody's a huggy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.07,1:02:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd get a dog or a kitty that I could hug up,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.36,1:02:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.36,1:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hug up a big storm all day,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.36,1:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.36,1:02:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.36,1:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And not look to people all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.36,1:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because a lot of people are going to think you're weird
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.36,1:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to touch them or hug them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.36,1:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.36,1:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.36,1:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.36,1:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.36,1:02:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying now to resolve it in myself of,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.36,1:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.36,1:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm going to go off and sit on a rock and stare.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.36,1:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.36,1:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.36,1:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if this keeps coming up,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.36,1:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.36,1:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the one thing that keeps pulling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.36,1:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.36,1:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the touch,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.36,1:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel the connection.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.36,1:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.36,1:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just like,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.36,1:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.36,1:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.36,1:02:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.36,1:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.36,1:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're reaffirming,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.36,1:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.36,1:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,reaffirming the affection,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.36,1:03:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.36,1:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.36,1:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so to transcend that is just basically,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.36,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.36,1:03:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is there,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.36,1:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.36,1:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.36,1:03:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,see,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.07,1:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.07,1:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.07,1:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're maintaining it by resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.07,1:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should give in to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.07,1:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.07,1:03:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.73,1:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a natural human proclivity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.73,1:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.73,1:03:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.11,1:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.11,1:03:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to change that,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.11,1:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.11,1:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.11,1:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.11,1:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,basically,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.11,1:03:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,go into it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.11,1:03:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.11,1:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,stop resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.11,1:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.44,1:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the craving be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.44,1:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.44,1:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,come to what you're seeking with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.44,1:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,reassurance,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.44,1:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,companionship,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.44,1:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling at one with others,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.13,1:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,overcoming a feeling of being on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.13,1:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.13,1:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.13,1:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,not being isolated or alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.13,1:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.13,1:03:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably serving multiple purposes all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.13,1:03:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.13,1:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from a really large family,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.13,1:03:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.13,1:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.13,1:03:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.13,1:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.13,1:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.13,1:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up in a family where kissing and all that wasn't really what boys did,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.13,1:03:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.03,1:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.13,1:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a different,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.13,1:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,different environment,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.76,1:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that she came from a cuddly,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.76,1:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,feely family.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.76,1:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.76,1:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.76,1:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.76,1:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.76,1:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.23,1:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.23,1:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.23,1:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.23,1:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.23,1:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.23,1:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.23,1:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just family.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.23,1:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.23,1:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's family patterning,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.23,1:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.23,1:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Family patterning.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.23,1:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.23,1:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.23,1:04:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.23,1:04:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.23,1:04:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.23,1:04:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been on,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.23,1:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been on anything but
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.90,1:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there's been a choiceless 40-year intense need to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.00,1:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.00,1:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,currently,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.90,1:04:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there is,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.90,1:04:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's energy that arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.90,1:04:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and it arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.90,1:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very pleasant,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.28,1:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.28,1:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and you,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.28,1:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,work,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.28,1:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,starts low and works all the way through and,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.28,1:04:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.28,1:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One works all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.42,1:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question coming here was that in parallel, it appears,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.15,1:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that in parallel to this more frequent energy that arises,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.40,1:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you termed it so beautifully, the surrounding of seduction.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.26,1:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this sense almost, how do you say it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.69,1:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this push-pull kind of a thing going on, it appears.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.11,1:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not something I'm familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.13,1:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's something that's being observed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.98,1:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know if there's a correlation between the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.55,1:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have noticed an increase in this experience of the energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.40,1:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have just also witnessed this different aspects that come
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.38,1:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and want to continue to stay in charge, in other words,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.25,1:05:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,on another lower level, you might say, of drives and so on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.61,1:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard you speak here, and you've mentioned several pointers.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.15,1:06:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you've said, in some context, it's to allow it and not resist it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.51,1:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps just observe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.26,1:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or in another context, it's to say, no, I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.21,1:06:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And refuse it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.23,1:06:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.96,1:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, being that this is being observed, which path would you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.36,1:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To refuse?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.55,1:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To refuse or to allow.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.86,1:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're ambivalent about it, I'd refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.82,1:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was none of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.61,1:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was none of your volition.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.01,1:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to comply with it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.05,1:06:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.36,1:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.11,1:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.40,1:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.21,1:06:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.65,1:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not just that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.94,1:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about entities.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.21,1:06:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.03,1:06:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels as though it's being.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.15,1:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I already answered it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.78,1:06:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's speaking of entities.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.84,1:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two separate.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.69,1:07:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the energy, which is very pleasurable, that comes up quite frequently.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.92,1:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.36,1:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the linear energy is perfectly normal and fine, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.59,1:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.53,1:07:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other is like a temptation of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.17,1:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.92,1:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.32,1:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say refuse the temptation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.40,1:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.90,1:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy is just kind of leaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.09,1:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.36,1:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.75,1:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, here's a call again.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.01,1:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.25,1:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if you'd be willing to calibrate this movie I'm trying to get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.88,1:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.80,1:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants us to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.01,1:07:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't calibrate things.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.51,1:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.84,1:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't do it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.28,1:07:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.65,1:07:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't because we get, sometimes we get wrong things when we calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.67,1:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's something I made?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.71,1:08:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.90,1:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the energy of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.88,1:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you made?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.15,1:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.13,1:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.69,1:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.84,1:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.90,1:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about your own product, whether it's good?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.40,1:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just want to know, it seems like there's a lot of blockage in this film going out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.47,1:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a film, it's a service film on addiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.42,1:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just thought I would try to get some more information on perhaps why it's not moving,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.03,1:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,why it's not going out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.22,1:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.85,1:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants us to calibrate the movie to find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.19,1:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.39,1:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a movie that she made.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.97,1:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.65,1:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's about addiction and she wants to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.84,1:08:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't, it doesn't seem to be going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.61,1:08:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, where do you want it to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.93,1:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it based on spiritual principles?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.42,1:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.53,1:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.53,1:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you want to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.06,1:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.76,1:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it to be in treatment facilities and jails and psychiatric wards.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.76,1:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you realize the competition you got, you got the world, decades of the world's experts
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.52,1:09:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're going to run into this and push them off the shelf and put yourself there?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.60,1:09:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.18,1:09:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.72,1:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.57,1:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.02,1:09:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a thing, a thing gains ground of its own quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.26,1:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you put it out there as being available.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.64,1:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring it up and whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.67,1:09:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, situations, it would be appropriate and then it seeks its own level like a quirk.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.60,1:09:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to struggle because the quirk comes to its own level of buoyancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.28,1:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the quirks without propelling it, without trying to make it do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.93,1:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's prepared and presented with love, that's all you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.35,1:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest takes place of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.43,1:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People will seek it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.71,1:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.39,1:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even getting invested interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.02,1:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to be objective.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.50,1:10:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel, once I've written it, my deed, my deed is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.39,1:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with it then, what the world does with it is their problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.52,1:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I just want to say it's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.85,1:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.44,1:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake your hand, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.42,1:10:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just going to ask one quick question and just if you had to give someone advice
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.86,1:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell them just one thing they had to hold in mind that would take them, if you could give it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.22,1:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing to hold in mind, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.01,1:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing to hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.98,1:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.28,1:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What would it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.56,1:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.17,1:10:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.44,1:10:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.10,1:10:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's all?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.47,1:10:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.86,1:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.30,1:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the answer you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.34,1:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the complete answer to every question.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.72,1:11:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no question that can't be answered by God.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.11,1:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.61,1:11:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Atkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.26,1:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.23,1:11:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.19,1:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to come for at least three or four years and today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.42,1:11:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.18,1:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.26,1:11:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.26,1:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.97,1:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.97,1:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.97,1:11:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.97,1:11:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.30,1:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.30,1:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Three or four years.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.30,1:11:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.39,1:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.39,1:11:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.35,1:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.60,1:11:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was blessed with finding that 12 steps 30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.60,1:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.60,1:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And it took me about six years to work on like my life depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.60,1:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.60,1:11:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that opened up a spiritual realm for me and then I finally went back to my
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.47,1:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Catholic roots, but then I started going on retreats and went beyond the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.22,1:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.60,1:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I started to look at religion, I mean the confines of the religion and that was
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.53,1:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.53,1:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the course of that, I was listening to tapes of some of the Catholic, like Keating
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.53,1:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and Pennington and I was, so I was really doing some Eastern practices in my prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.39,1:12:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.39,1:12:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, eventually, after hooking up with Stanislaw Grof, which caused some more interchange.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.39,1:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which caused what?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.39,1:12:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Grof.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.39,1:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Interchange.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.39,1:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I had a lot of experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.39,1:12:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hooked back up with the Catholic prayer, but because I couldn't find a retreat center
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.39,1:12:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in Las Vegas and I was always traveling to get a weekend retreat, there was a Buddhist
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.22,1:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,monk a mile away from me and I started going there and I went every day for about seven
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.89,1:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,years.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.89,1:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've had these wonderful experiences and learned a lot of things from both, but now,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.34,1:12:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I would never want to give up what I learned from Buddhism.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.65,1:13:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a great teacher and yet, I think what I did was I pushed away, I didn't push away,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.92,1:13:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I let go of the praying to God, because that's not what we did there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.19,1:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.19,1:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.19,1:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.19,1:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.19,1:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of praying to God?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.19,1:13:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.19,1:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And just did the practice of Vipassana.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.19,1:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the practice of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.03,1:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Vipassana, insight meditation with the breath.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.03,1:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.03,1:13:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.03,1:13:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, I'm at this place where I love both and yet, I'm 55 now and I'd like to find something
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.15,1:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that is more directive for me or that gives me more direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.34,1:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel pulled both ways and I-
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.34,1:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you feel the different ways?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.34,1:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels the pull of the Catholic religion and yet, she also feels the pull of the-
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.34,1:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so much the Catholic, it's, well, that's just it and why am I, I'm having
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.06,1:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,this conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.11,1:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.68,1:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having this conflict about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.68,1:14:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a group here when I first came to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.35,1:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They met where there's now a big resort and, where is that resort, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.05,1:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, down over the village.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.05,1:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilton.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.05,1:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilton.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.05,1:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.05,1:14:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 70 acres or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.05,1:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was a retreat center and it was run by an order of Catholic brothers, monks.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.77,1:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They called themselves Zen Catholicism.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.10,1:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And they had separate little places, everybody lived all by themselves, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.89,1:14:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They also had a meditation, Kiva, in the middle, with very thick brick walls and a thick carpet
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.22,1:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and one little window, absolute silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.22,1:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.22,1:14:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I went there for years and Sedona wasn't populated yet, you know, there's only 2,000
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.22,1:14:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or 3,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.40,1:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They called themselves Zen Catholicism.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.03,1:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when the population of Sedona began to increase, they moved up to Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.03,1:15:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of the town, Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.03,1:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowmass?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.03,1:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.03,1:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.03,1:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowmass is a different one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.03,1:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.03,1:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Benedictine, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.84,1:15:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you track them out, you can probably find where they moved to.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.84,1:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.02,1:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But theirs was a combination of the best of the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.02,1:15:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And they didn't see any conflict and I don't see any conflict either.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.02,1:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.02,1:15:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.02,1:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no conflict because truth is truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.47,1:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, what kind of wallpaper you put on it doesn't change the essence of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.47,1:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.59,1:15:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because the Buddha said don't use the term God, we did a diagnosis that the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.19,1:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.19,1:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.19,1:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.19,1:15:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.19,1:15:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.19,1:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha experienced the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.19,1:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.19,1:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.42,1:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you notice he didn't call it the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.42,1:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.42,1:16:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because otherwise he couldn't have reached a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.43,1:16:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He calibrates at a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.43,1:16:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to get to calibrate at a thousand is if you experience the reality of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.43,1:16:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.43,1:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So although he may verbally say don't use the term God because everybody is so cuckoo
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.50,1:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about the whole subject, you'll never get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.50,1:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be chasing your own definition.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.50,1:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotion then will take you to the ultimate truth either way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.50,1:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.50,1:16:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.50,1:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.50,1:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.61,1:16:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.61,1:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.61,1:16:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.61,1:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.61,1:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.61,1:16:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.61,1:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.77,1:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.77,1:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.77,1:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.77,1:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.31,1:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.82,1:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.82,1:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.82,1:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.82,1:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.76,1:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.85,1:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no conflict between the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.85,1:16:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because the Buddha said don't use the term God doesn't mean there isn't a God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.03,1:16:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He said don't talk that way because you'll be misleading people down all kinds of belief
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.52,1:16:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.21,1:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.39,1:17:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all the work you're doing and for helping make the non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.39,1:17:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.39,1:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.52,1:17:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question that has to do with my health.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.52,1:17:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've had a lot of eye problems in the last six years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.52,1:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple eye problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.52,1:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.52,1:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been in a spiritual path for many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.56,1:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to determine, and I've been working with teachers,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.36,1:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to discover if this is something karmic,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.25,1:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if this is something that's a lesson I'm trying to learn on my spiritual path,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.75,1:17:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or if I'm causing this on some level.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.01,1:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, what can I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.51,1:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already doing what you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.25,1:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're researching it on multiple levels simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.10,1:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you picture yourself, you picture the issue as resolving.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.81,1:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender to it if it is of a karmic nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.22,1:17:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender to it if it's karmic.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.48,1:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You do all of them at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.32,1:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, how do I surrender if it's karmic? I'm not sure I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.81,1:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you surrender what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.89,1:18:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I surrender to it if it's karmic?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.09,1:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I understood what you said. Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.02,1:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you surrender to anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.55,1:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, just turn it over to God, essentially?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.10,1:18:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go in to change it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.75,1:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it as healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.47,1:18:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.75,1:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it as the undoing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.36,1:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And accept it for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.39,1:18:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And ask for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.60,1:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the Course in Miracles?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.81,1:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known about it for 30 years, and it keeps coming up,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.18,1:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think it's time for me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.89,1:18:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a lot of miracles amongst groups of Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.77,1:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Recovery from all kinds of ailments and illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.61,1:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But not all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.93,1:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you say, many have a karmic component,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.19,1:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and they are serving a purpose, whatever is happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.22,1:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do what you can, physical, mental, and spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.75,1:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with that, the same as any other ailment, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.32,1:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.82,1:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, and then just surrender and release it,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.55,1:19:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and try not to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.89,1:19:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.39,1:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I tend to dwell on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.60,1:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.10,1:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Very good. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.85,1:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's possible, the recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.96,1:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See, some things are possible to recover,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.42,1:19:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,other things are not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.81,1:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things are just protoplasmic deterioration,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.72,1:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.63,1:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.32,1:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. But nothing seems to be possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.09,1:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. But nothing seems to be possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.28,1:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing seems to be hereditary or generic,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.39,1:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which is why it seems odd.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.39,1:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be anything that you can do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.81,1:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.18,1:19:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do what you can, physical, mental, and spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.01,1:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest is surrendered to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.75,1:19:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.72,1:19:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.18,1:19:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to God and your own karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.64,1:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.85,1:19:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to be here, and I am also a student
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.81,1:19:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Course in Miracles, but I have a medical question,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.76,1:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just about protoplasmic deterioration of the bones.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.00,1:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.26,1:20:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the best thing to do to get rid of osteoporosis?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.30,1:20:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it could be for you at a specific time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.30,1:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about osteoporosis?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.52,1:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.96,1:20:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You got an internist handling this?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.38,1:20:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my regular general practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.76,1:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bone scan.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.81,1:20:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a bone density?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.11,1:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.76,1:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It says that you got demineralization?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.80,1:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.38,1:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look into FORTEO, F-O-R-T-E-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.30,1:20:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.10,1:20:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look into FORTEO,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.23,1:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is parathyroid hormone injections.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.60,1:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That may increase the likelihood and rapidity of healing,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.76,1:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,plus enough calcium in the diet to take care
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.92,1:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the additional request.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.76,1:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask your doctor about FORTEO.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.76,1:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,FORTEO.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.34,1:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,F-O-R-T-E-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.84,1:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.22,1:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, these are shots.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.42,1:20:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.92,1:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A shot you got to give yourself every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.47,1:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the pill idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.80,1:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Parathyroid hormone, plus you take extra calcium.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.81,1:20:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's just something to look into.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.85,1:21:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the FORTEO.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.43,1:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,FORTEO.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.75,1:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.94,1:21:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just something to look into.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.86,1:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.98,1:21:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into FORTEO.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.89,1:21:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be an additional help in your case.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.73,1:21:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.31,1:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.92,1:21:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.53,1:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a thing called an anti-gravity machine,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.22,1:21:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which is used in space, which are up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.50,1:21:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Space station.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.31,1:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.02,1:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The bones will demineralize under zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.80,1:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So they have what they call an anti-gravity machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.39,1:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It recreates.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.47,1:21:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It imitates the impact of if you were on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.67,1:21:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's two things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.17,1:21:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,An anti-gravity machine and check out FORTEO.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.96,1:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two things together should make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.39,1:21:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.26,1:21:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say I told you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.30,1:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.50,1:21:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.00,1:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're writing a book somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.93,1:21:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the other day.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.97,1:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something on TV about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.38,1:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go blaming me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.38,1:22:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget how much it was then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.01,1:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.01,1:22:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.72,1:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.22,1:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.56,1:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.06,1:22:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So they are anti-gravity machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.56,1:22:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they're as expensive as they once were.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.73,1:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cheaper than a car anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.89,1:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, in your practice, how do you find the best way
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.43,1:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to balance the business world with the spiritual world
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.46,1:22:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and being in peace with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.23,1:22:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't see it as a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.89,1:22:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't see it as a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.88,1:22:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The business world is one way.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.22,1:22:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, they overlap.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.23,1:22:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They overlap.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.11,1:22:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one's conserved.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.27,1:22:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the other. In the business world you get the testing of how far you've gotten
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.03,1:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually and then in the spiritual world you get a chance to influence the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.22,1:22:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,business world by virtue of that which you have become. By virtue of that which
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.64,1:23:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you have become you begin to influence it. You know the famous book Jack, you
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.97,1:23:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,know Jack president of GE or GM or whatever. Yeah right. What he became you
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.31,1:23:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,know influenced the whole industry didn't it? Right. You remember your
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.47,1:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,picture of him there? I think he's in his late 60s and he's got a torso like, like
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.18,1:23:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,an athlete. You know what I say. You say well this guy was driven to perfection and so
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.68,1:23:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he stood as a role model of integrity and reaching the highest level of
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.10,1:23:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,performance you see. So
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.97,1:23:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.75,1:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't see the two as conflictual.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.52,1:23:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of spiritual alignment,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.82,1:23:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you may decline certain business opportunities
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.86,1:23:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that other people would avail themselves of.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.27,1:23:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would just say, I can't do that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.43,1:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But your department, maybe if you want to do that,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.30,1:23:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Milky Way, Cure Cancer,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.13,1:23:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,however you want to sell them and make money,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.52,1:24:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't do it, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.17,1:24:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You could decline it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.90,1:24:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But make sure they understand you're declining
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.64,1:24:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for the good of the company
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.67,1:24:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the good and welfare of the organization, too, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.09,1:24:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not just for your own personal weirdness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.53,1:24:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Can I have a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.56,1:24:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So they don't consider you a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.76,1:24:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them Holy Roller weirdo types.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.93,1:24:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's 50 cents for a smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.68,1:24:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.88,1:24:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.31,1:24:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sell you a blessing for 50 cents.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.92,1:24:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's merging spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.73,1:24:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a little business, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.47,1:24:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he just said, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.50,1:24:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.43,1:24:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, put it in the plate at church, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.64,1:24:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.14,1:24:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.14,1:24:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll sign it for me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.34,1:24:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.48,1:25:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this question has been asked before
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.48,1:25:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or if I missed it in one of your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.52,1:25:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible for someone to incarnate in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.90,1:25:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,be profoundly mentally challenged,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.90,1:25:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,almost non-verbal, and still be at 500?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.06,1:25:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.06,1:25:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You doubt it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.86,1:25:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sign it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.57,1:25:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about a person born deaf and dumb?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.57,1:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not deaf and dumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.57,1:25:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But they don't read or write and they don't speak very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.73,1:25:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the diagnosis, autistic or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.73,1:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.96,1:25:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some relative of yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.96,1:25:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.73,1:25:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had the privilege of being with a small group
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.73,1:25:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for quite a few months.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.73,1:25:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's one gentleman who just has a beautiful energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.73,1:26:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and twinkle in his eyes and kind of mischievous
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.73,1:26:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and he just seemed like he was very high vibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.84,1:26:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.22,1:26:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not really a matter of concern to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.22,1:26:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.22,1:26:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.22,1:26:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.22,1:26:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there's no resistance to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.22,1:26:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.22,1:26:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.57,1:26:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.57,1:26:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.57,1:26:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.57,1:26:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.11,1:26:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.11,1:26:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.11,1:26:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen Keller was born deaf, dumb, and blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.06,1:26:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I forget what she calibrated, 580 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.06,1:26:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.22,1:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.43,1:26:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the father of two daughters, third and fifth grade,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.43,1:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had a question about schooling.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.43,1:26:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a level of calibration that would be acceptable
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.43,1:26:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look for schools for your kids?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.43,1:26:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what I'd look for is at least in the 300s.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.43,1:27:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's willingness, helpfulness, cheerfulness,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.43,1:27:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a good ball team kind of energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.02,1:27:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The 300s, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.93,1:27:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And one other quick question that Mother would want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.93,1:27:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a risk with education getting stuck in the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.02,1:27:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the intellectualization?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.02,1:27:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's not due to the education.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.02,1:27:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the person's interest would stop there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.02,1:27:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not due to the education.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.13,1:27:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not due to the education itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.13,1:27:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.13,1:27:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.69,1:27:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.69,1:27:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.30,1:27:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.30,1:27:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.30,1:27:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you both for making yourselves available to us,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.30,1:27:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.30,1:27:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just like to ask for a moment of silent transmission
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.30,1:27:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,from my teacher and a photo.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.30,1:27:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.30,1:28:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.47,1:28:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.47,1:28:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.47,1:28:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I also have 50 cents for a smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.47,1:28:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't put your day job into play.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.47,1:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.92,1:28:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put them into play, to be sure, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.92,1:28:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.92,1:28:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You already answered my question,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.92,1:28:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just wanted to hold your hand and tell you I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.92,1:28:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.92,1:28:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.92,1:28:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.92,1:28:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.06,1:28:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're running really late.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.06,1:28:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this after I left.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.06,1:28:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this after I left in December at the airport, so you won't use it until next season, but it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.28,1:29:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyways, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.77,1:29:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.38,1:29:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.77,1:29:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorite time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.10,1:29:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.17,1:29:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.18,1:29:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.18,1:29:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.48,1:29:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our weakness, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.25,1:29:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be telling them that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.75,1:29:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the office, and everyone goes, oh, no, here she comes with a little thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.73,1:29:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to press this, and then they're going to sing all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.31,1:29:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have a weakness for these little toys like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.60,1:29:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you wouldn't have said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.68,1:29:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.85,1:29:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that we like Jell-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.47,1:29:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an old bathtub full of Jell-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.35,1:30:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They are cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.81,1:30:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They are, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.50,1:30:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They care for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.42,1:30:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.56,1:30:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been going through psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.43,1:30:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychoanalysis for about a year, and I recognize I'm sitting with so much anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.63,1:30:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like it's right here in my stomach all the time, and I realize now that it's been
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.52,1:30:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,there for pretty much my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.82,1:30:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like fear, anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.89,1:30:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It even came up great.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.60,1:30:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I wanted to ask this question, I almost turned away from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.27,1:30:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I'm comfortable to talk about it one-on-one, but in front of an audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.85,1:30:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it brings that same why it came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.51,1:30:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings that same feeling up of anxiety, fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.68,1:30:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of connected with that place that I'm walking around with.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.75,1:30:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the analysis, there's so many specific things that are coming up that I've never
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.68,1:31:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,even looked at before, but it comes up all the time, sometimes so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.39,1:31:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And at times, I want to sleep to avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.90,1:31:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.30,1:31:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, even to come up...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.38,1:31:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.07,1:31:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fearful anxiety, and it comes up sometimes when I'm doing things like...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.43,1:31:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How often do you see your therapist?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.03,1:31:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I used to see him like twice a week because it was in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.47,1:31:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to see him twice a week for about four hours for the week, and now, like I'm living
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.80,1:31:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in New York, so I do it on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.18,1:31:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I developed a comfort with him, so I didn't want to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.35,1:31:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a week for an hour now, hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.60,1:31:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's been really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.44,1:31:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's arduous, and I feel like I'm constantly in myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.01,1:31:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, it's always about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.64,1:31:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.31,1:31:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and I see value in it because I'm noticing things that I've denied before,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.81,1:31:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems like such a narcissist.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.81,1:32:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always about me, and I'm analyzing everything about myself all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.11,1:32:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a phase.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.35,1:32:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you understand the ego, you unravel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.65,1:32:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you take it apart once it's been unraveled, and you see how it's constructed and how it's
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.76,1:32:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,got that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.39,1:32:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you do more general spiritual work with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.00,1:32:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgive yourself for it being the way it is, and you allow yourself to be human.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.06,1:32:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You allow yourself to have defects if you want to view them as defects.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.34,1:32:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You view yourself as evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.19,1:32:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You view the understanding, first understand yourself, it says over the top of the, what
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.67,1:32:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to call it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.19,1:32:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Know thyself, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.73,1:32:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Know thyself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.53,1:32:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's an important period of investigation to know, understand, of course, what you're
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.88,1:32:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,investigating primarily is the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.92,1:32:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But to disassemble it is first to become familiar with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.26,1:33:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I think it's a good adventure you're doing to become more enlightened about your
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.07,1:33:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,own, the nature of one's own ego and how it got to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.81,1:33:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The contributions of the various people and the various cultures and value systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.23,1:33:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like there's like endless things to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.52,1:33:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, endless.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.23,1:33:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I get in, like, I've dealt with the father complex thing for a while because that was
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.84,1:33:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what I felt like was important.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.42,1:33:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see what you're talking about, overcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.27,1:33:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.76,1:33:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't a matter of overcoming.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.35,1:33:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of growing, transcending it, seeing the nature of it, and then letting
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.81,1:33:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.89,1:33:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, familiarizing with it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.92,1:33:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.42,1:33:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just becoming more familiar with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.38,1:33:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because insight itself tends to release you from the conflict, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.10,1:33:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.14,1:33:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Insight itself tends to release you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.53,1:33:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.35,1:33:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it has because I don't resent my dad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.47,1:33:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.27,1:34:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you have a dream and you understand the elements of the dream, then the conflict
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.02,1:34:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that the dream represents tends to resolve itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.30,1:34:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.80,1:34:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.60,1:34:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.68,1:34:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.10,1:34:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.26,1:34:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's important.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.14,1:34:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not refusing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.68,1:34:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not ignoring it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.18,1:34:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.64,1:34:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.23,1:34:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.80,1:34:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an actor, and I love what I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.85,1:34:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I find that it's my calling, and I have an idea that as an actor, sometimes I have to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.01,1:34:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,imagine horrible things and awful things, you know, imaginary circumstances, and I have
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.01,1:34:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,an idea that maybe that might be dangerous because you teach that, you know, whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.35,1:34:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold in mind, you manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.15,1:34:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it you have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.69,1:34:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this acting school or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.30,1:34:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like acting classes or when you're in a show and you're playing someone who's not
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.42,1:34:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who might be, you know, in a horrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.10,1:35:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're supposed to picture this ugly situation and let yourself respond to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.76,1:35:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's an artificial thing, it's just an image in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.19,1:35:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a movie, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.89,1:35:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why it's any different than a movie itself because it's optional.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.85,1:35:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've chosen to do that, so you're in control of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.56,1:35:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.94,1:35:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you also say that consciousness is naive, you know, and like every time I go to class
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.78,1:35:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or I...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.98,1:35:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I honor the work and then I feel depressed because I believe in the circumstances for
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.72,1:35:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that moment and for the next couple of days I'm depressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.39,1:35:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe in that which you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.38,1:35:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.80,1:35:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They become.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.34,1:35:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you become that which you're imagining.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.23,1:35:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.23,1:35:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.02,1:35:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any experience with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.81,1:35:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to have a strong sense of the reality of that which you are and see this other as
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.15,1:35:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,play.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.30,1:35:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And be able to...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.81,1:36:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, differentiate between the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.78,1:36:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One is play and the other is who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.88,1:36:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another quick question.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.97,1:36:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of embarrassed to ask this, but I also have another worry that once you leave
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.38,1:36:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this world, the average calibration of mankind will kind of go under, like below 205 or something
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.10,1:36:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's something that I worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.52,1:36:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something I worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.13,1:36:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We surrender the world to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.97,1:36:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we surrender the world to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.47,1:36:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And God's will is what manifests.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.40,1:36:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we surrender our will to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.81,1:36:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be, will be to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.00,1:36:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just surrender to thee, O Lord, who I surrender this world and my place in it and its destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.03,1:36:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.25,1:37:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is a perfect place for fulfillment of karmic potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.55,1:37:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For the undoing of the negative and the gaining of the positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.64,1:37:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In creating, surrendering the world to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.92,1:37:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been an enthusiast for saving the world for raids.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.10,1:37:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, they're too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.48,1:37:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last question.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.28,1:37:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was the last question.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.63,1:37:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got through answering it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.90,1:37:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.85,1:37:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again for the tremendous gift of being with you this entire day.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.13,1:37:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a wonderful gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.64,1:37:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To be with all such...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.30,1:37:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To be with all such wonderful people for a whole day.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.89,1:37:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our experience of each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.96,1:38:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of us has seen back and forth in the other one's eyes and reflected back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.44,1:38:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's his eyes looking to me and reflecting to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.14,1:38:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going to look into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.35,1:38:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They reflect back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.63,1:38:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So we become, there's a certain connectedness that goes back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.09,1:38:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we all become sort of in less than one unity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.77,1:38:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless us, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.68,1:38:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We give thanks to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.73,1:38:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For thy presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.17,1:38:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to thee, O Lord, for being allowed to be the teacher of such wondrous people.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.17,1:38:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.46,1:38:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought everybody had left.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.10,1:38:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out here and you're all still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.85,1:38:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you still be here if you just left?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.81,1:39:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not quite ready to detach.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.34,1:39:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, God love you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.47,1:39:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.38,1:39:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.15,1:39:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.52,1:39:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.06,1:39:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.68,1:39:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.47,1:39:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.27,1:39:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done, George.
